Mutability	Immutable (Fixed)	Mutable (Changeable)	Mutable (Changeable)
Thread-Safe	Yes	Yes (Synchronized)	No
Speed	Slow for modifications	Medium	Fastest
Use Case: Use StringBuilder for high-performance string manipulation (like building a long SQL query) unless you are working with multiple threads.
