Summary Table
Method	Type	Purpose
Filter	Intermediate	Removes elements based on a condition.
Map	Intermediate	Transforms elements into a new form.
Sorted	Intermediate	Reorders the elements.
Collect	Terminal	Gathers elements into a Collection (List, Set).
ForEach	Terminal	Performs an action for each element (no return).
Reduce	Terminal	Merges all elements into one single value.
